<LP>
   ASHLAND, Ky. -- Addington Environmental Inc. said it
signed an option to acquire an existing landfill in South
Carolina.
   The option allows Addington Environmental, a subsidiary of
the coal mining concern Addington Resources Inc., to purchase
the assets of Appleton Sanitary Landfill in Allendale County,
S.C., for an undisclosed amount.
